io.hekate.rpc

Interface RpcServerJmx


  • @MXBean
 @JmxTypeName(value="RpcServer")
public interface RpcServerJmx
    JMX interface for RpcServerConfig.

    Instances of this interface are registered to the JmxService for each combination of RPC interface (that is implemented by the RPC handler) and each tag (if specified)
